A vulnerability, which was classified as <a href="https://vuldb.com/?kb.risk">problematic</a>, has been found in <a href="https://vuldb.com/?product.orc:discount">Orc discount up to 3.0.1.2</a>. This issue affects the function <code>compile</code> of the file <em>markdown.c</em> of the component <em>Markdown Handler</em>. This manipulation causes uncontrolled recursion.

This vulnerability is tracked as <a href="https://vuldb.com/?source_cve.353138">CVE-2026-4833</a>. The attack is restricted to local execution. Moreover, an exploit is present.

The project maintainer confirms: &quot;[I]f you feed it an infinitely deep blockquote input it will crash. (...) [T]his is a duplicate of an old bug that I&#039;ve been working on.&quot;
